1. What is socket
  - Socket is technology help to comunicate between client and server in nearly realtime
  - Socket ussually apply to chat, live stream
  
2. Example
  - Consider we are using Facebook messenger
  - When user tap to one chat, app will subcribe to the chat channel using socket
  - As soon as it subcribe to the channel, it will receive a bunch of message since the last connection
  and start receiving and sending new message
